18:27.780 --> 18:29.220
And finally, there's some effort

18:29.220 --> 18:31.180
on all-in-one AI forecast systems

18:31.180 --> 18:34.100
that go directly from observations to forecasts

18:34.100 --> 18:36.420
to post-processing to produce predictions

18:36.420 --> 18:37.700
